Detailed Description

GPS measurements.

This struct contains GPS measurements required by MSL TRKR elements including pseudo range data. Based on OMA-TS-ULP V1.0.

Field Documentation

U08 RXN_GPSMsrElement_t::cNo

Carrier noise. Range 0 - 63.

Doppler. Range -32768 - 32767.

U16 RXN_GPSMsrElement_t::fracChips
